Mages...<br>
<br>
/flame off<br>
<br>
peeps make it more difficult than it needs to be.  Duel wield checks based on your off hands weapons delay.  Don't beleive me?  Put a stein or book in your main hand and attack something with your weapon in your off hand.  <br>
<br>
Guess what?  It is swinging based off of what delay?  That's right - your off hand delay from the weapon equiped.<br>
